TopicTitle: Photobomb on the way to Mun...

Articles.Content: I don't remember ever having all my guys outside at once. It was fun to set up. These are Muning, Shelden, and Hanbrett (Left to right)

Muning looks so scared!

Which was funny, because he got picked for this Mun trip just because of his name... he was my lander pilot, and looked that stressed every moment until splashdown. Well, he was happy on his munwalks... but otherwise, he's a little high-strung. So I'll keep him. those are my favorite guys.

Lol, i did the same with "Munwise Kerman" - he was wise in the ways of the Mun, so he was permanently stationed on the Mun.
I don't know why, but that picture makes me happy.

Nice picture!

I don't know why, but their facial expressions (one of them is scared, one of them has a huge grin on his face and one of them doesn't seem to care at all) kinda remind me of Jeb, Bill and Bob.
